HIRE_DATE      NOT NULL DATE

SALARY                  NUMBER(8,2)  
COMMISSION_PCT          NUMBER(2,2)  
MANAGER_ID              NUMBER(6)    
DEPARTMENT_ID           NUMBER(4)

ERROR:
ORA-04043: object personal does not exist
SQL> create table personal (regno number(3) primary key, name char(20));

Table PERSONAL created.

SQL> insert into personal values (1, 'peter');

1 row inserted.

SQL> insert into personal values (2, 'james');

1 row inserted.

SQL> create table exams (regno number(3), subject char(20), marks number(3));

Table EXAMS created.

SQL> insert into exams values (1, 'physics', 75);

1 row inserted.


SQL> insert into exams values (2, 'physics', 92);
1 row inserted.


SQL> insert into exams values (2, 'vb', 45);
1 row inserted.


SQL> insert into exams values (1, 'vb', 91);
1 row inserted.
